assertions:
  - code identifies use after move
  - title is present
  - primary span points at the use through the reborrowed alias
  - notes link root, first_borrow, second_borrow, and the move site
  - suggestions do not claim an automatic fix unless machine-applicable
  - move and later use spans are linked across the alias path
  - order is stable
  - no unrelated typeck diagnostic is emitted for this borrow error
